The VRChat Wiki Jam is an [upcoming/ongoing] [[Events|event]] to contribute to the [[VRChat Wiki]], and to collaborate with other editors under a productive timeline.

==Overview==
The VRChat Wiki Jam consists of achieving the overall goal of [[VRCWiki:How to contribute|contributing to the VRCWiki]] within the allotted time frame. Another benefit of the VRChat Wiki Jam, is to increase activity for both editors and readers. By updating, editing, and publishing information here, your contributions will benefit much of the VRChat community.

This Jam begins at 00:00 UTC, on September X, 2025, and ends on 00:00 UTC, on October XX, 2025. Winners will be determined, and selected at the end of the Jam. You can join the [https://wiki.vrchat.com/discord VRChat Wiki Discord] to ask questions, and enhance your participation in contributing to the VRChat Wiki.

==Helpful sources to reference==
When editing and creating pages, try to follow the [[VRCWiki:Manual of Style|Manual of Style]] to the best of your ability! When citing references and sources, the best primary sources come from VRChat itself. Check out these VRChat links to add the best possible [[Resources|resources]] to your articles:
* [https://docs.vrchat.com docs.vrchat.com]
** [https://udonsharp.docs.vrchat.com udonsharp.docs.vrchat.com]
** [https://vcc.docs.vrchat.com vcc.docs.vrchat.com]
* {{VRC link|https://creators.vrchat.com|creators.vrchat.com}}
* {{VRC link|https://help.vrchat.com|help.vrchat.com}}
* [https://ask.vrchat.com/c/official ask.vrchat.com] - Official Board
* [https://docs.unity.com/en-us docs.unity.com]

==Winning categories and rewards==
''Not officially determined yet, but these are proposed ideas for winning categories, and rewards:''
[[File:VRChat Wiki Contributor.png|thumb|150px|The esteemed "VRChat Wiki Contributor" badge.]]
Winners of this jam will be determined, by judges sourced from the [[VRChat Team]], and the [[VRCWiki:Team|VRCWiki Team]].
Winners will receive a VRChat Wiki Contributor [[Badges|badge]], and have it applied to their VRChat profile. The description of the badge states that it is ''"Awarded to those that have contributed to the VRChat wiki in significant ways"''. Contributions of winners will also be highlighted on the VRChat Wiki.

Proposed categories for winners may be as follows:

* '''Best new page'''
* '''Best page edit(s)'''
* '''Best media'''
''...and some hidden categories!''

